{"tid":457133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★加薪走下坡   I.T 行業　學歷越高薪酬越低！！！！","createTime":"2017-11-03T14:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T10:52:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5070d59badd307a496b967e23c701ec824d837","tid":457133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"個別工作範疇出現學歷越高，薪酬越低的情況，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊科技工作</span>，持碩士或以上學位只有14,406元，但持學士學位卻可達14,973元；又例如財務會計工作中，持文憑人士薪酬為11,693元，但持高級文憑/副學士人士薪酬卻平均低數十元，只有11,637元。除這兩個行業，市場拓展及銷售行業都出現「學歷越高，薪酬越低」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/126937/加薪走下坡-預計明年只增3-5-I-T-銷售行業-學歷越高薪酬越低\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F126937%2F%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E8%B5%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%9D%A1-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%AA%E5%A2%9E3-5-I-T-%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD-%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E8%B6%8A%E9%AB%98%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E8%B6%8A%E4%BD%8E&d=DInV5Kwn2B2D1XXUe0Kj0wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0972dcb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/126937/加薪走下坡-預計明年只增3-5-I-T-銷售行業-學歷越高薪酬越低</a>"},{"pid":"1c29f5dca39eeef7778a0acc1c03218dc03187b0","tid":457133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/915979/xlarge/15820291c3c423dd4565b35c409a9b5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F915979%2Fxlarge%2F15820291c3c423dd4565b35c409a9b5b.jpg&h=0a6a6ca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a76611e520b5afa22fdb754b914daee71610652f","tid":457133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"浸大人力資源策略及發展研究中心副主任葉偉光認為，大部分僱主都只會將僱員學歷按「有否讀大學」作為標準，至於是學士還是碩士不會太在意，「或者日後升遷會有影響，但入職基本上沒有分別。」安俊人力資源顧問有限公司董事總經理周綺萍亦指，除了需要進行研究或執教席，市面上大部分工作均不要求碩士學位，「學歷太高反而成為負擔，僱主會覺得你超出標準，會容易走。」"},{"pid":"1c3fa307e307fe33984802a76434657e7a0c2030","tid":457133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"多五百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n持碩士或以上學位只有14,406元，但持學士學位卻可達14,973元"},{"pid":"fe088662fc689a611938ab65ad8d841fe4846651","tid":457133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"none care<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa1aae0c8d9906a289f25784bbdd397883e3e97","tid":457133,"uid":59976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/MPRySX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FMPRySX.jpg&h=685f7f33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3af135135e4306d3ec5d5146414a491ee162cec2","tid":457133,"uid":90,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"Hk01，此post已完"},{"pid":"d41962c882d45a9042eb099d22c21be557056719","tid":457133,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"It=hope"},{"pid":"304f1cc1a2e0cc26008f5f990f009928d1a46b3b","tid":457133,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/b/b5/DrJim20120423rthk.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20140322133449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fb5%2FDrJim20120423rthk.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F300%3Fcb%3D20140322133449&h=ffd6976f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p